{title: Pickin' A Chicken}
{artist: Jim Reeves}
{composer: Written by Derek Bernfield, John Roberts, Trevor Boswell}

[C]Come to the barbeque and [G7]sit by my side
We couldn't chose a better [C]night if we tried
Can't you imagine what a [G7]thrill it will be
Pickin' a chicken with [C]me
